    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "description": "O2O 平台 P4 后端业务服务接口集；覆盖 8 大业务模块（Shop/Product/Marketing/Order/Payment/Finance/Dispatch/Review）+ Orchestration；累计 ≥ 40 用例，含外卖 9 节点端到端流程链。\n\n环境变量约定：\n  - {{baseUrl}}        http://localhost:3000/api/v1\n  - {{token_user}}     用户 JWT\n  - {{token_merchant}} 商户 JWT\n  - {{token_rider}}    骑手 JWT\n  - {{token_admin}}    管理员 JWT\n  - {{shopId}}         测试店铺 ID\n  - {{productId}}      测试商品 ID\n  - {{skuId}}          测试 SKU ID\n  - {{orderNo}}        测试订单号（端到端流程间共享）\n  - {{payNo}}          测试支付单号\n  - {{userCouponId}}   用户券 ID\n  - {{merchantId}}     商户 ID\n  - {{riderId}}        骑手 ID\n  - {{addressId}}      用户地址 ID"
  },
